# Student Marketplace

A campus marketplace for buying, selling, and renting items.

## Features
- Buy / Sell products
- Rental system with deposit
- Reels UI
- AI suggestions (planned)
- Real-time notifications (Socket.io)

## Tech Stack
- Next.js
- Node.js + Express
- MongoDB
- Socket.io

## Setup

### Backend
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev

### Frontend
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
